Package by.chmut.giftit.filter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthorizationFilter
    The Authorization filter class provides control over access to pages and execution of commands, according to user Role.
    EncodingFilter
    The Encoding filter class ensures that the correct encoding is set in all requests and responses processed.
    LocalizationFilter
    The Localization filter class provides installation of selected locale
    XssFilter
    The Xss filter class provides protection against XSS attacks.
    XssRequestWrapper
    The Xss request wrapper class extends the HttpServletRequest interface by overriding some methods to provide control over the XSS attack.
